654.question: What is the difference in performance between the interpretable system (e.g. vectors and cosine distance) and LSTM with ELMo system?
654.response: {'Answer': 'The interpretable system (e.g. vectors and cosine distance) has much lower perplexity than LSTM with ELMo system. But LSTM with ELMo system has much higher accuracy than the interpretable system.'}
654.answer: Accuracy of best interpretible system was 0.3945 while accuracy of LSTM-ELMo net was 0.6818.
